ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectOrder No. 172 - (Alberta) Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 172 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of ALBERTA with respect to the RAINSTORM which affected the Regional Municipality of Wood Buffalo, from June 7 to 11, 2013
